&gt; Yep April you are right. Remaining open to the possibility is hard  enough 
&gt; for most people. Again its a case of prove or disprove it for  yourself. Not 
&gt; everyone comes to the same conclusions or gets the exact  same results. 
&gt; Maybe similar but not exact. 
&gt;  
&gt; I tend to use a variety of methods. When voices come from things  such as 
&gt; water or out of thin air sometimes its a easier for some to  believe there is 
&gt; something there that they were not aware of.
&gt; 
&gt; But again they have to prove it for themselves to be able to have  that eye 
&gt; opening moment.
&gt;  
&gt; I only comment on what I hear or dont hear. My speaker set up is a  bit 
&gt; different than most. I hate headphones. Others prefer them. Some use  pc 
&gt; speakers. Results vary based on the individual. What I hear you may  not then 
&gt; again you just might hear it exactly the same. I dont worry  about that. Just 
&gt; keep exploring with an open mind.
&gt;  
&gt; Misty
